title: House speaker: Republicans challenge McCarthy for top job
text: > Florida House speaker: Republicans challenge McCarthy for top job Nominee for Speaker of the House and Oversight and Government Reform Committee Chairman Jason Chaffetz, R-Utah, left, arrives for a meeting with House Republicans on Capitol Hill in Washington, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015. Later in the day the House Republican caucus will vote on its nominee to replace House Speaker John Boehner, who is stepping down, and retiring from Congress, at the end of the month, after nearly five years in the role. (AP Photo/Jacquelyn Martin)
